[metadata]

Name:Test - Macro Replay - Dockside Sabertooth Tremors
URL:https://www.cardforge.org

Goal:Win

Turns:1

Difficulty:Rare

Description:Test puzzle for replaying a Treasure-funded bounce loop: Dockside Extortionist plus Temur Sabertooth plus Impact Tremors. Cast Dockside Extortionist from hand first to create the initial Treasures, then record one cycle that activates Temur Sabertooth returning Dockside Extortionist, casts Dockside Extortionist from hand using Treasure mana, and resolves the Dockside and Impact Tremors triggers. Repeat until Impact Tremors defeats the opponent.

